=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"拉布都要坐10碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293eedac0b223a2d66945f7f2683a438986f58f2","tid":2087190,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aae5107ba160abc3bd5b758ebb1cf763daf3fc7","tid":2087190,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"(二) 對香港特別行政區政府或者中央人民政府制定和執行法律、政策進行嚴重阻撓並可能造成嚴重後果；<br />\n舉慢少少手支持就中<br />\n<br />\n(三) 對香港特別行政區選舉進行操控、破壞並可能造成嚴重後果；<br />\n初選就中"},{"pid":"57a7e46a12f354b3cadc1b6f03e250ac7171166f","tid":2087190,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"推 7.1大遊行 tweet國際戰線 黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"4624d14ba73d000a59b9131acf84207ad8281d27","tid":2087190,"uid":266503,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"c2a2f0805517d5b7e6903fba4699d53757c261e1","tid":2087190,"uid":150547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"074fb453a612ab0cc9791dbe02c7a5dac93eaae3","tid":2087190,"uid":103981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"444c73c6c69e4f402094caa32a7a500346c10647","tid":2087190,"uid":41116,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"第六十二條 香港特別行政區本地法律規定與本法不一致的， 適用本法規定。<br />\n<br />\n咩都可以用支安法告<br />\n佢話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"咁到底會唔會有死刑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"理論上冇<br />\n實際你會因為反對政府感到慚愧而自殺"},{"pid":"c2b62465bf111a3635b37d1256d97fa17530f6ba","tid":2087190,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢條叫萬能老屈法</span><br />\n<br />\n100%入罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab84040ac473a79d0506bb6a6fbd0cb5cdb8cbc2","tid":2087190,"uid":284630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"338a1cc0154f6732bdc3bdcad7a6cd228796aaf3","tid":2087190,"uid":46933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"投反對票禁完制即刻拉得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"國安法講得冇錯, 議員有投反對票既一次性自由"},{"pid":"aacda67c0e2f25b694e636a18e19488fd0f351a1","tid":2087190,"uid":150547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b8d21a25a9d1493cc51b1c8d8881c86b09791c1","tid":2087190,"uid":40804,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T